MBC Block Explorer

This is a PHP (no database required) block explorer designed for use with mini-blockchain coins.

IMPORTANT:

The full blockchain is required for this explorer to work properly.

REQUIREMENTS:

* PHP >= 5.4
* cryptonited > 14080613

INSTALLATION:

* upload files to server
* run /install/install.php
* follow install instructions
* edit /inc/config.inc.php
